  "texts": [
    "ViT extracts features across the entire image without degrading image resolution, preventing spatial loss from information skipping.",
    "Thus, ViT is ideal for brain imaging analysis.",
    "The self-attention strategy of ViT has the capacity to accurately capture the interdependencies between various dispersed networks of brain regions 21.",
    "ViT is based on the concept of Transformers from natural language processing (NLP) applied to medical images.",
    "It uses a standard Transformer architecture, with minimal modifications, to process MRI images instead of text."
  ],
